Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.26,2160P思源-e,,0,0,0,,It was about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.26,0:00:05.28,2160P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Jeremy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:25.11,2160P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Twenty-five years and my life is still,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:29.91,2160P思源-e,,0,0,0,,Trying to get up this great big hill of hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:34.48,2160P思源-e,,0,0,0,,...for a destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:40.11,2160P思源-e,,0,0,0,,I realized quickly when I knew I should,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:44.74,2160P思源-e,,0,0,0,,that the world was made up of that brotherhood of man...
